{"tid":282553,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己老母好港女","createTime":"2017-06-13T12:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T13:21:17.000Z","uid":99771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cef936ab218a11ac9742998a007f48517c989b5","tid":282553,"uid":99771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"成日好小事就發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如 夏天屋企買大支裝果汁返嚟大家飲<br />\n咁過左幾日乜都飲曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢自己又唔早啲飲 就屌我地飲曬唔留俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又例如 有時佢㩒鐘 我幫佢開門<br />\n一開閘就屌我唔幫佢拎嘢 叫我快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬啊我都睇唔到你拎住嘢點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一嚟就屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人分享下老母既港女事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701ec357f15f1a22b647e7694e0dc63c2ac40032","tid":282553,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"無港女點生你個港仔啊？"},{"pid":"93b5f71974616dd8626d2d009c8c554d19d563af","tid":282553,"uid":3421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"邊個會覺得自己呀媽係鬼婆賓賓泰妹？"},{"pid":"1976e954ba4e193520afc10d40be23b4d56c564f","tid":282553,"uid":99771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無港女點生你個港仔啊？</blockquote><br />\n絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36c28c9bc8cbcdf7d0e8a1689893dd4322bc856","tid":282553,"uid":99771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個會覺得自己呀媽係鬼婆賓賓泰妹？</blockquote><br />\n公主病囉好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83db8aeb727e83f71d9f8e5e5f9cd6b06f205af","